{"type": "article", "id": 31034, "title": "拿这个小犀牛锤子当桌面装饰品吧！｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-08-15T23:01:12Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 31532, "name": "Split Grain"}, {"id": 31533, "name": "iThinking"}, {"id": 31534, "name": "Moskou"}, {"id": 31535, "name": "Cube 44"}, {"id": 31536, "name": "Paul Foeckler"}, {"id": 31537, "name": "Yunus Emre Uzun"}, {"id": 31538, "name": "Marta Adamczyk"}, {"id": 31539, "name": "Pavel Vetrov"}, {"id": 31540, "name": "Anthony Guex"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 155, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160815234125W4hDrfEyXw3g7YFU.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。<br></p><h3>Sliced Firewood Light by Paul Foeckler</h3><p>还记得我们上周介绍的用<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/30911.html\">废弃木料制作的灯具</a>吗？来自美国加州的设计师 Paul Foeckler 同样利用当地木材推出了一系列极简风格的落地灯，在造型上更是大胆地采用了切片设计，甚至还能清晰地看到树木的年轮。这些灯具由三个部分组成，中间的切片通过三根铝制细管连接在一起，打开后灯光就会从上下溢出，看起来非常温暖。你可以从他经营的网店 <a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/shop/SplitGrain\" rel=\"nofollow\">Split Grain</a> 购买到这些灯具，售价从 350 到 2450 美元不等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160815234424NVCgOo0rJct96Dbi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.853000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160815234425yfb4zwMst8DV7eGY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.959000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160815234424lAGmfFkEw83Rb1og.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.039000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160815234424fjOMu82dQDhkmpyq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.074000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160815234425VKio8OU5Dasn9f6w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.248000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160815234425MIV4gCpnJA1sfNEX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.503006\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Rhino Hammer by iThinking</h3><p>来自台湾的创意家居品牌 <a href=\"http://www.ithinking.com.tw/\" rel=\"nofollow\">iThinking</a> 最近推出了将工具与家居摆设合二为一的锤子 Rhino Hammer，希望以这种小巧温暖的造型改变人们对于工具的刻板印象。犀牛本体采用铝合金制成，搭配把手的磁铁可以巧妙地把高碳钢伸缩杆隐藏起来，使用时只要将头部拔出再拉出把手即可。Rhino Hammer 的尺寸比一般铁锤要小，这只可爱的小犀牛平时可以作为装饰或是当做纸镇使用。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1538570791/rhino-hammer\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，早鸟价为 38 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160815234356bHaRYSwIyNet1grd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562592\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160815234354akxmiKjCISL6Bv0X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562592\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160815234354RmhEQMl3BXt6NxnD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562592\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160815234354lHXno2QLw78INvOF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160815234354p1MtuqvyilkB4Lsc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Perforé Side Table by Yunus Emre Uzun</h3><p>这张名为 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/41412965/Perfor-Side-Table\" rel=\"nofollow\">Perforé</a> 的边桌是土耳其设计师 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/emreyunusuzun\" rel=\"nofollow\">Yunus Emre Uzun</a> 的作品，利用三种不同材质的搭配打造出了简洁干净的外形。边桌由一个方正的黑色金属支架支撑，顶部则由大理石台面和黄铜制杂志架两部分组成，有一种自成一体的和谐感。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160815234313qmukUGew9odFJHN0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562857\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608152343085lhSpCfoktn9vGFu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016081523431051924feiZ7JuSPXL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160815234314zkDG5jRdxSIUqBi6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>K1 by Moskou</h3><p>由波兰设计师 Marta Adamczyk 创立的 <a href=\"http://moskou.pl/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Moskou</a> 工作室主推极简风格的设计，这把名为 <a href=\"http://moskou.pl/chair/\" rel=\"nofollow\">K1</a> 的椅子是她的最新作品。它的轮廓干净利落，从侧面看就像是一个不规则的几何图形。椅背和座位采用了厚实的橡木板，与纤细的金属框架形成了鲜明的对比。如果你感兴趣的话可以通过<a href=\"http://moskou.pl/kontakt-architektura-wnetrz-warszawa\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>与 Adamczyk 联系进行订购。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608152342334FAtJpovamV5wIQu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500726\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160815234233OTMlDao5gt4e1Hzy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160815234233wzLVlENkBnpGoJ3A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160815234236epz6fA1cnOdsJW3r.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160815234236RiOnWG8rTxALbHq3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.501333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Horizon-Bookcase by Pavel Vetrov</h3><p>设计师 <a href=\"http://www.pavelvetrov.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pavel Vetrov</a> 最近为乌克兰家具品牌 <a href=\"http://www.cube44.com.ua/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Cube 44</a> 推出了一个名为 Horizon 的家具系列，其中最吸引人眼球的或许就是这个由金属框架和木质搁板组合而成的书架。Vetrov 延续了他见长的简约风格，巧妙地将框架分为两个部分，使它看上去清爽明快。你可以通过 Cube 44 的<a href=\"http://www.cube44.com.ua/shop/\" rel=\"nofollow\">网店链接</a>购买，售价根据大小分别为 14900 和 16200 格里夫纳（约合人民币 3949 和 4293 元）。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160815234217Q0nICaD84xRBdONW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562857\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160815234218A4VhZR9BG31nWDrK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608152342180oZPgLeDFKkxwmIA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>The Illusionist by Anthony Guex</h3><p>这个名为 The Illusionist 的果酱包装设计是加拿大设计学生 Anthony Guex 的作品。Guex 巧妙的设计让它看上去只容纳了一瓶果酱，顾客只有通过包装外附带的纸锯从当中“锯”开才能发现“真相”。包装一旦解体之后，纸锯还可以从中对半分开当作标签挂在果酱瓶口，非常有趣。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160815234147eYnZ1oDjR2zivdgq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.688750\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608152341470YkArtwhIPzEf5nv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.732500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160815234148GQFbj7xAI8hHCn9L.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160815234147f6Jtj0kGABmPO2qF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.773750\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}